      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\">\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"1062\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220286/RenderMan_Lama_Surface.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330560734&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1062&amp;height=527\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542220286/RenderMan_Lama_Surface.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330560734&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"636\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542220304\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Lama_Surface.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542220286\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"bab44b55-181d-46c0-9bb1-9723b98d6096\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220286/RenderMan_Lama_Surface.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330560734&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1920&amp;height=954 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220286/RenderMan_Lama_Surface.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330560734&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1062&amp;height=527 1x\"></span><p><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">All MaterialX Lama materials need to begin with attaching a LamaSurface node to your geometry.</span>  <br/><br/>LamaSurface allows you to create a material and define different materials for the front and back facing surface. <br/><br/></p><hr/><h3 id=\"LamaSurface-MaterialProperties\">Material Properties</h3><p><strong>Material Sides</strong></p><p>Defines the number of sides a material has, 1 (default) or 2 where a backside can be a different material look.<br/><br/></p><div class=\"embeddedObject conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"false\" data-layout=\"default\" data-local-id=\"112ed833-6beb-4908-ba8f-53ff5cb1b102\" data-macro-id=\"6ecb2107-c9c2-40a6-ad82-3688c8993264\" data-macro-name=\"multimedia\">\n    <video src=\"/wiki/download/attachments/542220286/RenderMan_GoldLeaf.mp4\" height=\"380\" width=\"100%\" autoplay=\"\" controls=\"\">\n        Your browser does not support the HTML5 video element\n</video>\n\n</div><p><br/>The above example demonstrates a leaf material on the front side and a gold material on the back side, creating ... GoldLeaf<br/><br/></p><p><strong>Material Front</strong></p><p>This is the material that defines the front facing result.<br/><br/></p><p><strong>Material Back</strong></p><p>This connection is available if the Material Sides is set to 2 and defines the look of the backside of the surface.<br/><br/></p><p><strong>Presence</strong></p><p>This connection is available if enabled in the Features below. This connection allows you to define the visibility of a surface using a pattern connection.</p><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"1310\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220286/Lama_presence.00001.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330560956&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1310&amp;height=736\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542220286/Lama_presence.00001.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330560956&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"720\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542220307\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Lama_presence.00001.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542220286\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"258d3376-2fbb-49f5-bcb1-ff442ff89c16\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220286/Lama_presence.00001.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330560956&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1920&amp;height=1080 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220286/Lama_presence.00001.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330560956&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1310&amp;height=736 1x\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"1310\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220286/Presence_header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330560956&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1310&amp;height=736\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542220286/Presence_header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330560956&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"720\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542220313\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Presence_header.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542220286\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"425eeecf-bc03-410e-875d-345e7220321f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220286/Presence_header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330560956&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1920&amp;height=1080 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220286/Presence_header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330560956&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1310&amp;height=736 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"695\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220286/Presence_R.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330561208&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=695&amp;height=390\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542220286/Presence_R.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330561208&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"720\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542220316\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Presence_R.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542220286\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"ef78091a-754a-4a4e-a200-53f384e00094\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220286/Presence_R.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330561208&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1390&amp;height=780 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220286/Presence_R.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330561208&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=695&amp;height=390 1x\"></span><p /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" width=\"695\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220286/Presence_Phasor.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330560956&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=695&amp;height=390\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542220286/Presence_Phasor.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330560956&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"720\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542220310\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Presence_Phasor.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542220286\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"d64681f4-01f9-4038-9728-0af9af1118e4\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220286/Presence_Phasor.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330560956&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1390&amp;height=780 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220286/Presence_Phasor.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330560956&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=695&amp;height=390 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<hr/><h3 id=\"LamaSurface-Features\">Features</h3><p><strong>Compute Presence</strong></p><p>Allows the creation and connection of a presence setting or connected pattern to control the visibility of the object.<br/><br/></p><p><strong>Compute Opacity</strong></p><p>This enables or disables the computation of opacity for transmissive materials (like glass). Leaving it off can speed up a render for possible draft or preview renders.<br/><br/><strong>Presence / Opacity Cached </strong><br/><br/>Whether the renderer should cache presence (and opacity) or not. Caching these properties will lead to faster tracing, especially for shadow queries, but can lead to a less sharp result than uncached presence/opacity. (Note that checking either subsurface or interior computation will automatically disable presence/opacity caching.)<br/><br/></p><p><strong>Computer Subsurface</strong></p><p>This enables or disables the computation of subsurface scattering (when in use). Leaving this off can speed up draft or preview renders.<br/><br/></p><p><strong>Compute Interior</strong></p><p>This enables or disables the computation of the interior for transmissive materials (like glass). Leaving it off can speed up a render for possible draft or preview renders. If enabled, the Compute Opacity control also needs to be enabled.</p><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
    }
  },
